medialog.abovecontentportlets
==========================================



Features
--------

- adds portlets above content
- adds portlets below content


Installation
------------

Install medialog.abovecontentportlets by adding it to your buildout::

    [buildout]

    ...

    eggs =
        medialog.abovecontentportlets


and then running ``bin/buildout``
